    {
        "content": "<p>We used these in <a href=\"https://www.cs.ox.ac.uk/people/samuel.staton/popl24.pdf\">this paper</a> (accepted at the POPL conference, conditionally). We have some methods for building them. From the perspective of categorical probability, the paper is about a correspondence between Markov categories of a certain kind and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graphon\">graphons</a>. (We've been at it for a while, and I mentioned some preliminary results at the CPS workshop in 2020.)</p>",
